<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Dear Sir/Ma'am,</p>
    <p>
      This is to inform you that your ward, <%= @student.first_name %> <%= @student.last_name %>, was found engaging in <% @point.description %> in the campus and a total of <% @point.value %> points have been deducted from this disciplinary points. We will have no other option but to request you to withdraw him from the school if he is found repeating the same offense.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      This is for your immediate attention. Please login to the site to see your ward's disciplinary points at <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Yours sincerely,</p>
    <p>School Administration.</p>
  </body>
</html>